Package tools

Class Vector

  • java.lang.Object
    • tools.Vector
  • public class Vector
extends java.lang.Object
    2-dimensional vectors. Instances of this class are immutable: a vector, once defined, cannot be modified. Operations on vectors produce new vectors as results.
